messages.content: Hey there! This is EZ Mobile Mechanic. What's going on with your vehicle?
I didn't quite catch that. Could you please repeat what you said?
I understand. Could you tell me what's wrong with your vehicle?
um and you my oil changed
Got it, you need an oil change. Can you please provide the year, make, and model of your vehicle?
Thank you for the information. To confirm, you have a 1996 Geo. I can text you an estimate for the oil change. Would you like that?
